---
import myself from "../assets/images/Cartoonify.svg";
import myself3 from "../assets/images/myself.jpg";
---

<div class="wrap sm:flex-col rounded-lg offscreen relative">
 
  <h3 class="py-5 font-[mono] text-4xl text-center offscreen hover:tracking-[.51vw] hover:text-[tomato] text-[var(--text-primary)]">
    About<span class="animate-ping">_</span>
  </h3>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center offscreen">
    <div class="foto-swich">
      <img src={myself.src} class="sm:w-[100%] opacity-100" alt="foto of colin" />
      <img src={myself3.src} class="sm:w-[100%] " alt="foto of colin" />
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
      <div class="content-box">
        <div class="language-switcher">
          <h3 class="content-header2">
            Who am I 
            <span class="animate-ping"> ?</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="lang-buttons">
            <button type="button" class="lang-btn active" data-lang="en">EN</button>
            <button type="button" class="lang-btn" data-lang="de">DE</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="language-content active" id="content-en">
          <p class="p-6">
            Hello! <br />I'm Colin, a 38-year-old passionate web developer. Since my
            youth, I've been a true PC nerd with a strong affinity for technology. <br
            />Besides my work as a web developer, I'm also an avid gamer and love
            spending my free time on challenging games. Additionally, I have a
            special passion for bonsai art, which helps me bring calm and balance to
            my daily life. 
            With my diverse experience and wide-ranging interests, I bring creative
            and functional solutions to my projects. Whether it's developing a
            user-friendly website or solving complex technical challenges, I am
            always motivated to achieve the best results and help my clients reach
            their goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="language-content" id="content-de">
          <p class="p-6">
            Hallo! <br>
            Ich bin Colin, ein leidenschaftlicher Webentwickler. Seit
            meiner Jugend ein PC-Nerd mit einer Affinität für
            Technologie. Neben meiner Arbeit als Webentwickler bin ich auch ein begeisterter
            Gamer und verbringe gerne Freizeit mit anspruchsvollen Spielen. Zusätzlich
            habe ich eine Leidenschaft für die Bonsai-Kunst, die mir hilft,
            Ausgleich in den Alltag zu bringen. Mit meiner vielfältigen Erfahrung
            und meinen breitgefächerten Interessen bringe ich kreative und funktionale
            Lösungen in Projekte ein. Egal ob es darum geht, eine benutzerfreundliche
            Webseite zu entwickeln oder komplexe technische Herausforderungen zu lösen,
            ich bin immer motiviert, die besten Ergebnisse zu erzielen und meinen Kunden
            zu helfen, ihre Ziele zu erreichen.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-box ">
        <h3 class="content-header">
          Self Proclamations<span class="animate-ping">_</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="skills-container">
          <div class="skill-item">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-keyboard"></i>
            <span>Web Developer</span>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-item">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>
            <span>UI/UX Enthusiast</span>
          </div>
          <div class="skill-item">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i>
            <span>Bonsai Enthusiast</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const langBtns = document.querySelectorAll('.lang-btn');
    const langContents = document.querySelectorAll('.language-content');
    
    langBtns.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const lang = btn.getAttribute('data-lang');
        
        // Update active button
        langBtns.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
        btn.classList.add('active');
        
        // Update active content
        langContents.forEach(content => {
          content.classList.remove('active');
          if (content.id === `content-${lang}`) {
            content.classList.add('active');
          }
        });
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .wrap {
    width: 100%;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    padding-top: 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 100vh; 
    height: fit-content;
  }
  
  img {
    width: 30%;
    max-width: 250px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    outline: 1px solid var(--border);
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 15px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    transition: outline-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: mono;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 3px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--text-titel);
  }
  
  p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: .5s;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 5vw;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .content-box {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 768px;
    background-color: var(--form-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .language-switcher {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  
  .lang-btn {
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: mono;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-titel);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .lang-btn:hover {
    color: tomato;
  }
  
  .lang-btn.active {
    border-color: var(--border);
    color: tomato;
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
  }
  
  .language-content {
    display: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(10px);
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
  }
  
  .language-content.active {
    display: block;
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  
  .content-header {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .content-header2 {
    background-color: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    width: 70%;
  }
  .content-header:hover,
  .content-header2:hover {
    letter-spacing: 0.51vw;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .skills-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }
  
  .skill-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    flex: 1 0 30%;
    padding: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    font-family: mono;
  }
  
  .skill-item i {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  
  .skill-item:hover {
    color: tomato;
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  
  .foto-swich {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 200px;
    border-radius: 0px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .foto-swich img {
    width: 200px;
    transition: .5s;
  }
  
  .foto-swich:hover img:nth-of-type(2) {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  
  .foto-swich:hover img:nth-of-type(1) {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  
  .foto-swich img:nth-of-type(2) {
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    opacity: 0;    
  }
  
  .foto-swich img:nth-of-type(1) {
    transform: translateX(50%);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .skill-item i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .content-box {
      width: 95%;
    }
    
    p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .skills-container {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .skill-item {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .content-header {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .lang-btn {
      padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes ping {
    75%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
  
  .animate-ping {
    animation: ping 1s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;
  }
</style>
